{"tid":93090,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過有deja vu感覺？","createTime":"2017-01-24T06:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T22:09:04.000Z","uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d543e7be8c489e9fa4cad8817ac799e2ae757fb2","tid":93090,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊討論下？你嘅case係點？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我由幼稚園開始一直有deja vu嘅情況<br />\n電影trailer，日常片段，好多野都可以deja vu<br />\n曾經中學有段時間持續困擾過我一年有多 <br />\n日日夜夜出現 <br />\n幾確定自己係夢入面見過某啲野 但係冇人信<br />\n每次依種感覺出現就會想嘔同暈<br />\n之後少左但係keep住過一排就會有<br />\n<br />\n近排又發作<br />\n種感覺係無時無刻都可以出現<br />\n近幾次直情係係夢入面作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  起身差啲唔出黎<br />\n好辛苦"},{"pid":"f1d25fea14c578ab2b2a668751d19a60ce534bf0","tid":93090,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"有 明明應該係第一次見嘅野會覺得以前曾經見過"},{"pid":"dfc72a471f058677f9a62b1e92f555b26657aa97","tid":93090,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"就黎變月經<br />\nbtw試過 不過細個出現次數多啲 宜家好耐先一次"},{"pid":"bef257dfe862e3f2603dc1975866f7dc93d25cfe","tid":93090,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"El Psy Congroo"},{"pid":"239f3b26c80e60381a08b05ff8399b922a442791","tid":93090,"uid":17807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"既視感？"},{"pid":"3dddc9a8f49d0c42ef948a1df4ef23ab6c30dfc9","tid":93090,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就黎變月經<br />\nbtw試過 不過細個出現次數多啲 宜家好耐先一次</blockquote><br />\n我都係"},{"pid":"c825244f563f6cf8171008431edcb2198ac8dfae","tid":93090,"uid":49032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"經常有"},{"pid":"7559427169c7410d9c8d302f581c4d36cace6951","tid":93090,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:58:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人都係會好頭痛頭暈同作嘔？"},{"pid":"c0f9eac89bad8a9dcbadaf981a4287a883a45017","tid":93090,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"差唔多日日都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f51c48f1a8acd7aecb4c69021ded6f075fb0a02","tid":93090,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差唔多日日都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱又有 好想嘔 差啲暈低"},{"pid":"e452d3583287e5b0fc46552611ecdad588124def","tid":93090,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T20:02:24.000Z","msg":"(中文)<br />\n<br />\n穿梭水泥牆相縫隙，到底想逃到裡 <br />\n如何逃出無所不在的空間 <br />\n在交雜恐懼與憎恨的小行上 <br />\n邪惡勢力笑著說：「人類已在掌握之中」 <br />\n　 <br />\n連鏡中的自己都笑了，在水泥的縫隙之間 <br />\n不知在哪裡看見兩人的愛情與執著 <br />\n邪惡勢力笑著說：「人類已在掌握之中」 <br />\n　 <br />\n連你，至連你都費人疑猜，忘了心，死了心 <br />\n　 <br />\n未來，過去，現在，人類的連續劇   D&eacute;j&agrave;vu<br />\n腳本總是似曾相識 <br />\n重複的是無能承擔傷害的你 <br />\n　 <br />\n死、生、現實、生、死、瞬間、無能的我不斷重複"},{"pid":"af64928d3fd35066c573d2112932e7e67bb07322","tid":93090,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T22:09:04.000Z","msg":"沖涼成日唔記得洗左頭未<br />\n諗下仲死 太多想似嘅沖涼經歷干擾自己<br />\n最後又要洗多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知算唔算其中一種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}